COPY 3

234
00:15:25,008 --> 00:15:27,928
and cooperated with Kira,
tape number three was to be aired.

235
00:15:28,387 --> 00:15:30,013
And if the answer was no,
number four was to be aired.

236
00:15:30,013 --> 00:15:30,305
COPY 4

237
00:15:30,389 --> 00:15:33,016
COPY 3

238
00:15:33,016 --> 00:15:33,183
Tape three details the conditions
for cooperation.

239
00:15:33,725 --> 00:15:37,312
Basically,
to broadcast more criminals.

240
00:15:37,896 --> 00:15:40,357
Especially those who had hurt people...

241
00:15:40,441 --> 00:15:42,901
Or criminals who had abused
those weaker than they are.

242
00:15:42,985 --> 00:15:44,403
Regardless of how severe
their crimes were.

243
00:15:45,404 --> 00:15:47,614
And Kira would play the judge
in all of this.

244
00:15:48,657 --> 00:15:52,327
Furthermore, as proof that
the police are cooperating...

245
00:15:52,578 --> 00:15:55,497
he said that he wanted
the top brass from the NPA and L

246
00:15:55,581 --> 00:15:58,917
to appear on TV and announce
that they will cooperate with him.

247
00:16:00,794 --> 00:16:03,589
In other words, get the top brass
and me, to show our faces

248
00:16:03,672 --> 00:16:08,051
so that if we do anything suspicious,
he can kill us.

249
00:16:09,136 --> 00:16:13,098
So, what if we had answered no?

250
00:16:13,765 --> 00:16:16,602
Basically the same thing,
just expressed in a different manner.

251
00:16:17,644 --> 00:16:20,898
Mr. Yagami, the answer is no,
of course.

252
00:16:21,315 --> 00:16:26,195
Please give Sakura TV permission
to air the fourth video.

253
00:16:27,404 --> 00:16:31,158
<i>I think it is unfortunate...
that your answer is no.</i>

254
00:16:31,617 --> 00:16:33,076
<i>The police have answered...</i>

255
00:16:33,160 --> 00:16:34,786
<i>that they still wish
to fight me.</i>

256
00:16:34,995 --> 00:16:38,290
<i>So I will first take the life of
the Director-General of the NPA.</i>

257
00:16:38,373 --> 00:16:43,670
<i>Or, Imay take the life of the L
who is leading the investigation.</i>

258
00:16:44,630 --> 00:16:48,717
<i>The Director-General or L.
Who will be sacrificed...</i>

259
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:51,261
<i>for the loss of a peaceful world?</i>

260
00:16:52,429 --> 00:16:54,181
<i>Please make your decision in four days.</i>

261
00:17:04,358 --> 00:17:06,485
As I thought,
god is really on my side...

262
00:17:07,402 --> 00:17:09,154
Only this time, it's not god

263
00:17:09,238 --> 00:17:10,322
but a Shinigami, a God of Death.

264
00:17:11,532 --> 00:17:12,783
So <i>it seems.</i>

265
00:17:13,617 --> 00:17:16,578
Another Shinigami has come
to the human world.

266
00:17:17,246 --> 00:17:19,206
And another Shinigami's Death Note...

267
00:17:19,289 --> 00:17:22,292
has fallen into the hands of
someone who endorses Kira.

268
00:17:22,459 --> 00:17:25,379
SAKU RA TV

269
00:17:25,379 --> 00:17:25,671
This guy probably also
has the Shinigami-eyes.

270
00:17:26,672 --> 00:17:30,717
So this Kira's killing abilities
are far more powerful than mine.

271
00:17:31,468 --> 00:17:34,221
If I leave things
the way they are,

272
00:17:34,304 --> 00:17:36,640
I might be eliminated
within the next four days.

273
00:17:37,474 --> 00:17:38,725
But...

274
00:17:38,809 --> 00:17:41,395
I can't forgive the impostor
for dragging

275
00:17:41,478 --> 00:17:43,939
down Kira's image
with these dirty tactics.

276
00:17:44,690 --> 00:17:46,775
If the impostor slips up
and is caught,

277
00:17:46,858 --> 00:17:49,736
the existence of the Death Note
could be discovered... That would be bad.

278
00:17:50,028 --> 00:17:52,364
I can't let them run wild
for too long.

279
00:17:55,367 --> 00:18:00,581
My priority is to cooperate
with the investigation...

280
00:18:00,706 --> 00:18:04,126
and to figure out L's moves and
the fake Kira's moves.

281
00:18:08,672 --> 00:18:11,049
Ryuzaki, it's as you thought.

282
00:18:11,758 --> 00:18:14,469
Leaders of several countries
have talked and

283
00:18:14,553 --> 00:18:17,389
they want the real L
to appear on TV.

284
00:18:20,392 --> 00:18:22,728
That would be the most right
and reasonable choice.

285
00:18:23,687 --> 00:18:25,731
Well, we still have three days,

286
00:18:26,106 --> 00:18:27,858
so let's think of a measure
to prevent all that.

287
00:18:28,358 --> 00:18:30,193
It would annoy me...

288
00:18:32,195 --> 00:18:35,032
if I'm killed by someone who's
jumped on Kira's bandwagon.

289
00:18:36,241 --> 00:18:37,784
What are you talking about Ryuzaki?

290
00:18:39,745 --> 00:18:42,497
There is a high possibility
that fh/ls Kira is a fake.

291
00:18:43,165 --> 00:18:46,168
No, we should call him
the Second Kira.

292
00:18:46,418 --> 00:18:47,836
The Second Kira?!

293
00:18:48,420 --> 00:18:51,590
W-Why do you think
there's a second Kira?

294
00:18:51,840 --> 00:18:53,800
Please explain!

295
00:18:54,468 --> 00:18:58,930
First of all, there are
the predicted victims.

296
00:18:59,014 --> 00:19:02,100
They were used to convince
the TV station employees that he's Kira.

297
00:19:02,934 --> 00:19:04,853
Those two victims
were only featured

298
00:19:04,936 --> 00:19:08,065
in women's magazines and
on daytime talk shows.

299
00:19:08,732 --> 00:19:12,486
The real Kira has no need to prove
himself with such insignificant people.

300
00:19:13,028 --> 00:19:16,114
But in the Second Kira's view...

301
00:19:17,616 --> 00:19:20,077
he couldn't use a criminal that

302
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:22,788
the real Kira might kill
before his prediction.

303
00:19:23,163 --> 00:19:25,165
Hmm... Ryuzaki...

304
00:19:25,540 --> 00:19:28,669
What are the chances that
there is a second Kira?

305
00:19:29,461 --> 00:19:32,005
This time it's more than
a 70% chance.

306
00:19:33,465 --> 00:19:35,759
I don't like the way he does things.

307
00:19:36,134 --> 00:19:37,302
It's not like Kira.

308
00:19:37,386 --> 00:19:38,553
"Not like Kira"?

309
00:19:38,970 --> 00:19:41,723
Kira has always avoided
innocent victims,

310
00:19:41,807 --> 00:19:44,267
aside from those who have
tried to catch him.

311
00:19:45,352 --> 00:19:47,062
If we catch one Kira,

312
00:19:47,145 --> 00:19:50,774
I think we'll get a hint as to
how we can catch the other.

313
00:19:52,818 --> 00:19:53,902
Mr. Yagami.

314
00:19:54,444 --> 00:19:58,073
May I ask your son to
cooperate in this investigation?

315
00:19:59,366 --> 00:20:03,453
Does that mean he's
no longer a suspect?

316
00:20:03,870 --> 00:20:09,584
No. I can't say that he's been cleared,
but I could use his reasoning abilities.

317
00:20:10,502 --> 00:20:11,962
<i>So that's what it means.</i>

318
00:20:13,046 --> 00:20:16,216
If my son wants to cooperate with you,
I have no reason to stop you.

319
00:20:17,008 --> 00:20:19,261
Thank you. But...

320
00:20:20,011 --> 00:20:25,100
please keep it a secret that
this current Kira might be a fake.

321
00:20:25,892 --> 00:20:28,979
Please make it seem as if
we're pursuing the same Kira.

322
00:20:36,027 --> 00:20:37,320
Hey, Misa...

323
00:20:37,696 --> 00:20:39,906
I gave you the Death Note...

324
00:20:40,407 --> 00:20:43,869
so why don't you use
it more for yourself?

325
00:20:44,244 --> 00:20:46,246
I am using it for myself.

326
00:20:46,371 --> 00:20:48,331
Because I believe in what Kira is doing.

327
00:20:48,915 --> 00:20:51,293
I want to know what kind
of person Kira is.

328
00:20:51,793 --> 00:20:53,837
I want to meet and talk to him.

329
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:57,924
I sent those videos to
the television station just for that.

330
00:20:58,008 --> 00:21:00,385
I made sure
Kira would take notice.

331
00:21:01,428 --> 00:21:04,431
I bet that got Kira's attention.
I'm sure of it.

332
00:21:05,265 --> 00:21:06,850
This is a dangerous game.

333
00:21:07,601 --> 00:21:10,562
You might be killed.
Do you understand?

334
00:21:11,438 --> 00:21:15,567
It's all right. I'm sure that Kira
is kind to those with pure hearts.

335
00:21:16,109 --> 00:21:17,444
But if it comes down to it...

336
00:21:17,736 --> 00:21:20,614
I'm stronger because
I have the eyes!

337
00:21:23,116 --> 00:21:26,161
TO BE CONTINUED

338
00:21:26,536 --> 00:21:31,500
<i>I dreamed a dream
that no one could see,</i>

339
00:21:31,583 --> 00:21:36,880
<i>I threw away everything
that I didn't need</i>

340
00:21:37,005 --> 00:21:40,425
<i>I'm holding these feelings</i>

341
00:21:40,509 --> 00:21:45,889
<i>That I can't give up in my heart</i>

342
00:21:46,014 --> 00:21:52,270
<i>Even if my feet fall victim
to the shackles of sacrifice</i>

343
00:21:52,354 --> 00:21:56,858
<i>In between reality and my ideal</i>

344
00:21:57,651 --> 00:22:02,531
<i>I can't hold back
the flooding impulses</i>

345
00:22:02,781 --> 00:22:06,159
<i>Because I have a strong desire</i>

346
00:22:06,243 --> 00:22:09,996
<i>To accomplish</i>

347
00:22:10,622 --> 00:22:15,210
<i>[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]</i>

348
00:22:15,377 --> 00:22:20,924
<i>I'm not weak enough to believe</i>

349
00:22:21,007 --> 00:22:25,971
<i>Any of these negative perceptions</i>

350
00:22:26,429 --> 00:22:31,768
<i>I'm a trickster
who doesn't know solitude</i>

351
00:22:36,106 --> 00:22:38,108
PREVIEW

352
00:22:38,108 --> 00:22:39,526
I need to find out
about the Fake Kira

353
00:22:39,609 --> 00:22:43,113
before anyone else on
the Task Force does.

354
00:22:43,738 --> 00:22:48,326
What kind of person are you,
Fake Kira?!

355
00:22:48,410 --> 00:22:51,121
NEXT EPISODE: LOVE

